OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and breezy with rain and
OL,6,Fdrizzle slowly clearing, but lingering
OL,7,Fin the south. Some brighter spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping in the north with sunshine
OL,9,Fand scattered showers, some heavy and
OL,10,Fwintry over higher ground. Feeling
OL,11,Fwarm in the south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLight rain clears most areas
OL,14,Fexcept the far south before returning
OL,15,Fnorth later. Elsewhere clear spells
OL,16,Fwith northern showers, wintry on
OL,17,Fhills. Patchy frost in Scotland,
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland and England.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
