OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FStorm Dave moves northwards
OL,6,Facross Northern Ireland and western
OL,7,FScotland, bring cloud, rain and strong
OL,8,Fwinds. Coastal gales likely here, but
OL,9,Fdrier further south. Stay windy but
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
